  <source>University of Padua</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate the role of balneotherapy in obese patients with knee
      osteoarthritis in terms of pain relief, improving joint function and deambulation, on
      endocrinological parameters, quality of life and of reduction the costs to &quot;Servizio
      Sanitario Nazionale&quot; (NHS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
